### API Documentation & Test Requests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/jiocoders/v1

### 1. Hello API (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hello
Accept: application/json

### 2. Hello API with Name (Public)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/hello
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "jiocoders"
}

### 3. Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "admintemp",
    "password": "password"
}

### 4. Admin: Get All Users
# Requires Basic Auth or Session (using admintemp:password for demo)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Basic admintemp password
Accept: application/json

### 5. Admin: Get Specific User
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/user/admintemp
Authorization: Basic admintemp password
Accept: application/json

### 6. Admin: Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Authorization: Basic admintemp password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "newuser",
    "password": "newpassword",
    "email": "newuser@example.com",
    "role": "USER"
}
